  <exercise label="objects_exercises-ex-4">
    <statement>
      <p>Add a definition for the <pf>getPerimeter</pf> function in <pf>Rectangle</pf>. Your code will be inside the class.</p>
    </statement>
      <program interactive="activecode">
        <preamble>
